ğŸ“Œ Description :

This project is an educational Python application that records keyboard activity and periodically captures screenshots with explicit user consent.
The program associates keystrokes with corresponding screenshots based on time intervals.

ğŸ§  Project Purpose :

The goal of this project is to understand:

Keyboard event handling

Multithreading in Python

Screenshot automation

Time-based data association

Ethical data collection with user consent

ğŸ§° Technologies Used :

Python

pynput (keyboard listener)

