âš™ï¸ Features :

User consent popup before execution

Keyboard logging with timestamps

Screenshot capture at fixed intervals

Automatic session folder creation

Association of keystrokes with screenshots

Multithreaded execution

â–¶ï¸ How It Works :

The user is asked for consent before logging begins

Keyboard input is recorded with timestamps

Screenshots are taken at regular intervals

Keystrokes occurring between screenshots are associated and logged

All data is stored in a session-specific folder

ğŸ” Ethical Notice :

This project is created strictly for educational and learning purposes.
User consent is mandatory, and the application should only be used in controlled, authorized environments.

ğŸ“ Learning Outcome :

By completing this project, one gains hands-on experience with:

